sentences: He graduated from Ateneo de Davao University before trying his luck in Manila with his band, Extreme Mix, now known as Myxtreme.
He has also provided backing vocals for artists such as Luke Mejares and Jay-R. His debut album was released in 2004 by Evolution Music, distributed by Warner Music.
He was able to perform as front act for David Foster at the Araneta, won an Awit Award in 2004 for Best Collaboration with Nina, and another award in 2005 for the cut Kasalanan Nga Ba?"
